365. Langenbecks Arch Chir. 1979 Nov;350(1):33-42. doi: 10.1007/BF01232093.

[Primary carcinoma of the extrahepatic bile ducts (author's transl)].

[Article in German]

Neugebauer W, Durst J, Mayer HR.

From 1957--1977 193 patients were treated at the surgical clinic of the 
